  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to evaluate the attenuation of ischemic-reperfusion injury in the liver after
      sevoflurane preconditioning. In the presence of sevoflurane, an attenuation of liver injury
      is hypothesized (diminished increase of liver enzymes, reduced production of inflammatory
      mediators).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Organ protection; preconditioning; volatile anesthetics; ischemia reperfusion
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
